nks\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.corpusthomisticum.org/\">Corpus Thomisticum</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.corpusthomisticum.org/it/index.age\">Web-based Index Thomisticus search engine</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://itreebank.marginalia.it/\">Index Thomisticus Treebank</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.allc.org/about/people/honorary-members#FatherBusa\">Association for Literary and Linguistic Computing - Honorary Members</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.digitalhumanities.org/\">Digital Humanities WebHome</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,867529,00.html\">Religion: Sacred Electronics</a> <i>Time Magazine</i>, Dec. 31, 1956.</li></ul>\n<div role=\"navigation\" class=\"navbox\" aria-labelledby=\"Authority_control_frameless_&amp;#124;text-top_&amp;#124;10px_&amp;#124;alt=Edit_this_at_Wikidata_&amp;#124;link=https&amp;#58;//www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q718355&amp;#124;Edit_this_at_Wikidata\" style=\"padding:3px\"><table class=\"nowraplinks hlist navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;color:inherit\"><tbody><tr><th id=\"Authority_control_frameless_&amp;#124;text-top_&amp;#124;10px_&amp;#124;alt=Edit_this_at_Wikidata_&amp;#124;link=https&amp;#58;//www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q718355&amp;#124;Edit_this_at_Wikidata\" scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\"><a href=\"/wiki/Help:Authority_control\" title=\"Help:Authority control\">Authority control</a> <a href=\"https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q718355\" title=\"Edit this at Wikidata\"><img alt=\"Edit this at Wikidata\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/73/Blue_pencil.svg/10px-Blue_pencil.svg.png\" width=\"10\" height=\"10\